{
  "stem": "2533.1",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, we saw two black dots behind the fences of the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were coming closer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, we heard two children calling for their parents.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And father-- the grandfather and the parents, they were the twins.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were probably really left with some people to-- to look after them or something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the two dogs tore the kids apart while the parents and all of us were standing on this side of the fence, and we couldn't help.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So then I knew from that day on what the Germans are capable of.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I still took it a little bit light because my mother remembered the First World War how the German soldiers helped-- helped them when the Russians withdrew and all of that.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She couldn't believe that from angels in 20 years could turn out to be such-- I don't know how to call them because if I call them beasts, I will insult the beast.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because a beast only kills when he's hungry or when he is attacked.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it was worse.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So and then not too long after, the 20's of December, we told we were not going to work anymore.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had to stay and beg, and farmers come along with horse-driven wagons.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were taken out from that camp from Staw.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were driven.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't that far.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were driven with-- on horse-driven wagons.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were-- we didn't walk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were told to take-- we didn't have much of belongings anymore in the ghetto because we couldn't even go back to get clothes-- anything from the house, but we managed, you know.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People-- the secretaries, we knew them very well.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
